{"tid":2278568,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<表態> Ted Cruz：若法律戰打到上最高法院　特朗普仍可獲勝","createTime":"2020-11-09T08:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T14:44:16.000Z","uid":227801,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e105cbb880998c4007a2b446de294ffa8bc4faf8","tid":2278568,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E5%85%8B%E9%AD%AF%E8%8C%B2-%E8%8B%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%88%B0%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%9D%E5%87%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2585%258B%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%258C%25B2-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=795ffdea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2585%258B%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%258C%25B2-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&h=f352e831\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E5%85%8B%E9%AD%AF%E8%8C%B2-%E8%8B%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%88%B0%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%9D%E5%87%BA/</a><br />\n代表民主黨參加美國總統大選的拜登宣布勝選後，尋求連任的美國總統特朗普指大選點票不公，其團隊表明要在本周展開大規模訴訟，特朗普團隊已在周末就亞利桑那州點票提出訴訟。霍士新聞報道，特朗普盟友、共和黨參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）認為，如果特朗普的團隊能夠把法律戰打到上最高法院，則仍然有可能勝選。<br />\n克魯茲接受霍士新聞節目訪問時說，「我相信總統特朗普仍然有通往勝利的路，那就是每一票都要點，並且不要計偽造及不合法的選票。我們有法律程序去決定什麼是合法，什麼是不合法。」特朗普在 Twitter&nbsp;上轉載克魯茲訪問片段，Twitter&nbsp;同時加上警告字句指，選舉舞弊的指控受爭議。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲舉例，在密歇根州就發現點錯票的情況，數千投給特朗普的選票，一度錯誤計入拜登得票。他說，密歇根州 47 個縣城都使用同一點票軟件，這必須要檢視，又說：「我們很難知道事實、真相，這案將很容易被送到最高法院。」<br />\n克魯茲說，2000 年的大選，布殊同戈爾就曾因得票相距太少而交由最高法院處理：「我相信今次程序亦大致如此，即使媒體告訴大家放棄、回家吧，但事情不是這樣做的，我們知道心中想誰贏，我們要遵守法律，這意味要允許法律程序展開。」<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"576eb088807ab8e213fee1b2f017de4c47b4cf0b","tid":2278568,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48fdf5dd4763ad20ad15bc9d445eda394bab6bf","tid":2278568,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c0886d77386c5f4c7fab04a886c51b7dac8127","tid":2278568,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"最高法院有冇得駁回上訴?"},{"pid":"743c04a901d704673cb1f1d34bb3f7078bd0ee02","tid":2278568,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"don't give me hope<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bbcf912987737011359d3218e2da8170374e6e","tid":2278568,"uid":227801,